{"tid":1639262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 巡演《Love, Poem》門票開賣　光州場一分鐘售空！","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T15:31:42.000Z","uid":34643,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf0edae0d49aaf2d539955b0a240ef17112b5d6","tid":1639262,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:39:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3.orbi.kr/data/file/united2/c150837e-2f83-4e33-98e3-10eaaa0f843f20190802_001120.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.orbi.kr%2Fdata%2Ffile%2Funited2%2Fc150837e-2f83-4e33-98e3-10eaaa0f843f20190802_001120.jpg&h=f82f2a91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://s3.orbi.kr/data/file/united2/84e5c40e-6b30-426e-a145-ff028aad552f20190802_001139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.orbi.kr%2Fdata%2Ffile%2Funited2%2F84e5c40e-6b30-426e-a145-ff028aad552f20190802_001139.jpg&h=2cf4ffb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU 的年底巡演即將開跑，首場門票毫不意外地火速售罄，希望 Uaena 們都能順利買到其他場次的票囉！<br />\n<br />\nIU 昨晚經由 MelOn Ticket 開賣了亞洲巡迴演唱會《Love, Poem》的光州場門票，結果在短短一分鐘內就被搶購一空，再度印證了票房威力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-10-08/120825-777985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-10-08%2F120825-777985.jpg&h=7b04f2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以 11 月 2 日的光州場為起點，IU 的《Love, Poem》也將陸續前往仁川 (11/09)、釜山 (11/16) 和首爾 (11/23~11/24) 舉行。<br />\n<br />\n進入 12 月後，IU 就會來到台灣開啟海外場次，目前在 12 月 28 日前已敲定的場次依序有新加坡、菲律賓、馬來西亞、泰國和印尼，最近一定要記得關注售票資訊哦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/a/2019-10-08/120825-777986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fa%2F2019-10-08%2F120825-777986.jpg&h=f58bf541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://data.whicdn.com/images/332507696/original.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdata.whicdn.com%2Fimages%2F332507696%2Foriginal.jpg&h=a6fb070e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75504f535b83bd5c11bd2c2016